{"tid":1820915,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國防部今年內在太平洋部署特遣部隊 針對中國","createTime":"2020-01-11T22:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T00:13:16.000Z","uid":125193,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"00414833e6dec2fbd47448e38a1bdd83e6cb132d","tid":1820915,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T22:15:23.000Z","msg":"美國陸軍部長麥卡錫表示，美軍計劃在未來兩個財政年度，在太平洋地區的台灣及菲律賓以東島嶼，部署兩支特遣部隊，將具備執行針對中國及俄羅斯的情報、電子、網絡、導彈等任務的能力。<br />\n<br />\n麥卡錫表示，美國一旦與其他大國發生衝突，未能輕易轟炸戰略目標和安全運送部隊，為了令美國取得上風，陸軍特遣部隊能為海軍和空軍開路，為聯合作戰部隊的推進創造條件，提供遠程精准火力和功效，包括高超音速精準打擊導彈，電子戰和網絡攻擊能力。<br />\n<br />\n麥卡錫相信，特遣部隊有能力改變部分來自中國和俄羅斯，意圖阻止美國艦艇靠近亞洲大陸的力量，有助壓制中俄的軍力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502192-20200111.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502192-20200111.htm&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWd5VMZmAwfp0CD4JwUII9h4%3D&h=7d08f1db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502192-20200111.htm&h=19cda7ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502192-20200111.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7d5906548db1060c992bbcd700bea8e48fb28932","tid":1820915,"uid":169646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T22:16:01.000Z","msg":"美軍來了我帶路 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596b544fb2ffd883a9f7a386bdd816fe455dcdd1","tid":1820915,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T22:16:25.000Z","msg":"幾時打柒班香港狗"},{"pid":"11d5d3a04cfe2f9cc0888ed48313a5fdb97ca3a5","tid":1820915,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T22:17:36.000Z","msg":"台灣捱過左呢次，又有更多美軍幫手，又有反滲透法，算係大步檻過"},{"pid":"b25a99f50c8efb8816c64ca10848c0c5d088c96b","tid":1820915,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11d5d3a04cfe2f9cc0888ed48313a5fdb97ca3a5","tid":1820915,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":0,